Argued and submitted April 28, reversed and remanded June 14, 2006 STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. STEPHANIE DEANNE ROBERTS, Appellant. 040165FE; A125025 136 P3d 1229 Seann C. Colgan, Assistant Attorney General, argued the cause for respondent. With him on the brief were Hardy Myers, Attorney General, and Mary H. Williams, Solicitor General. PER CURIAM

Rosenblum, J., vice Richardson, S. J.

Ernest G. Lannet, Deputy Public Defender, argued the cause for appellant. With him on the brief were Peter A. Ozanne, Executive Director, and Peter Gartlan, Chief Defender, Legal Services Division, Office of Public Defense Services.

Before Haselton, Presiding Judge, and Armstrong and Rosenblum,* Judges.
